text:
Studying until the last minute, huh?
Impressive, Juri.

It's the first stage with all of 283PRO,
so there's no room for mistakes.

You're dependable.
And it seems like you're not nervous.
Oh, now that you mention it, maybe.

As we practice together, the feeling of enjoying it
becomes stronger than any anxiety or worry.

I believe that with everyone,
it'll definitely be a great stage.

Yeah, I think so too.
I'm looking forward to the stage after this.

Yeah,
don't miss a single moment of it!
